    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Hi, I'm Sarah.</h1>
    <p>A lawyer who taught herself to build software with AI, and now runs a legal tech startup solo. I'm here to get you over the same first hurdle someone once got me over.</p>
  </div>
